text: Blabia meinerti is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1900. It is known from Colombia and Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Blabia meinerti. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Blabia Category:Beetles described in 1900
